oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Faculty Senate Meeting Minutes February 10, 2006
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: University of Denver
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Faculty Senate Meeting Minutes from February 10, 2006. This meeting was called to order by President Potter at noon and continued as follows: Academic Planning Committee, Personnel Committee, Finance Committee, Student Relations Committee, Nominations Credentials and Rules, All Undergraduate Student Association (AUSA), Interim Provost's Remarks, Teaching Task Force Report with discussion and motion, New Business and the meeting was Adjourned at 1:40pm.
